reviews.text:
Really fun location with multiple vendors. 

I had to try the Brunch Rice Bowl with chicken adobo. Started with the amazing waffle with maple syrup....

Ok place,  worth a try!

Felt like trying something light and easy going and the tofu skewers hit the spot. Crispy with a nice sweet and salty drizzle sauce...
The food is good. The service is excellent. The ambiance is okay. I would say it's a tad pricey for a bowl. It's about $20 for what you can get at other...
